Topic: troubleshoot

Troubleshooting

No search results:
  Try fewer keywords, remove restrictive `--type` filters, or inspect the archive with `spinedigest index <archive.sdpub>`.

Missing generated objects:
  Queue the relevant generation task for the chapter:
    spinedigest queue add <archive.sdpub> --chapter <id> --task reading-graph --accept-cost
    spinedigest queue add <archive.sdpub> --chapter <id> --task summary --accept-cost

Need machine-readable output:
  Use `--json` or `--jsonl` on object commands.
